body:
See issue #1605.
Needs more testing and probably also more compile time checks.

commit.message: Initial attempt at implementing read-only memoryviews. (Github issue #1605)
Fix compiler crash when index base does not have an 'entry'.

commit.message: Add dedicated test file for read-only memory views.
Add minimal documentation for const memory views.
Avoid side-effects of auto-pickling in error test.
Disable auto-detection of read-only memory views (too unsafe) and acquire them only as read-only if the memory view dtype is a "const" type.
Fix memoryview assignment from const view to const view.
Repair memslice test after disabling auto-detection of read-only views, but keep some of the tests for 'const' views as smoke tests.
Clarify doc section on const memoryviews.

title: implement read-only memoryviews
